32-1404.Initiative and referendum petitions; signers; requirements.

Initiative and referendum petition signers shall conform to the requirements of sections 32-629 and 32-630.

SourceLaws 1994, LB 76, § 386;Laws 1995, LB 337, § 4;Laws 1997, LB 460, § 7;Laws 2003, LB 444, § 12;Laws 2008, LB39, § 5;Laws 2015, LB367, § 2;Laws 2025, LB521, § 76.Operative Date: September 3, 2025
